 Nam l\u00e0 bao l\u00e2u?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/lam-sao-mua-ho-hang-hoa-tu-han-quoc-huong-dan-chi-tiet-tu-a-z\/#Co_the_dat_hang_so_luong_lon_khong\" title=\"C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng?\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/lam-sao-mua-ho-hang-hoa-tu-han-quoc-huong-dan-chi-tiet-tu-a-z\/#Dich_vu_co_ho_tro_doi_tra_hang_khong\" title=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng?\">D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-5'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/lam-sao-mua-ho-hang-hoa-tu-han-quoc-huong-dan-chi-tiet-tu-a-z\/#Lam_the_nao_de_theo_doi_don_hang\" title=\"L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng?\">L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vi_sao_nen_su_dung_dich_vu_mua_ho_hang_hoa_tu_Han_Quoc\"><\/span>V\u00ec sao n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mua h\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\">Mua h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n, quy tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch thu\u1ebf quan. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mua h\u1ed9:<\/p>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c: B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ngu\u1ed3n h\u00e0ng, t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t mua hay lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ee7i ro: C\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb mua h\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn tay an to\u00e0n.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 thanh to\u00e1n: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 website H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 thanh to\u00e1n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, mua h\u1ed9 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd: C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty mua h\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i khi v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"NHBLogisticscom_%E2%80%93_Don_vi_mua_ho_hang_hoa_uy_tin_tu_Han_Quoc\"><\/span>NHBLogistics.com \u2013 \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb mua h\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a uy t\u00edn t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4049 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"650\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order.png 1080w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-1024x1024.png 1024w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-370x370.png 370w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-120x120.png 120w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-840x840.png 840w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/order-410x410.png 410w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>NHBLogistics.com l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 mua h\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, NHBLogistics cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 mua h\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n, nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Uu_diem_cua_NHBLogistics\"><\/span>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a NHBLogistics:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c website H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<\/li>\n<li>Thanh to\u00e1n h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 gi\u00e1 minh b\u1ea1ch.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang th\u1eddi gian cam k\u1ebft.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n vi\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 24\/7.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_mua_ho_hang_hoa_tu_Han_Quoc_tai_NHBLogisticscom\"><\/span>Quy tr\u00ecnh mua h\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i NHBLogistics.com<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_1_Gui_yeu_cau_bao_gia\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: G\u1eedi y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u00e1o gi\u00e1<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin sau cho NHBLogistics:<\/p>\n<ul data-spread=\"false\">\n<li>Link s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n mua.<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, k\u00edch c\u1ee1 (n\u1ebfu c\u00f3).<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_2_NHBLogistics_bao_gia_va_xac_nhan_don_hang\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: NHBLogistics b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, NHBLogistics s\u1ebd t\u00ednh to\u00e1n gi\u00e1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, ph\u00ed v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, thu\u1ebf v\u00e0 ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 chi ti\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_3_Thanh_toan_don_hang\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: Thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u00e1, b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn. NHBLogistics s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng ngay sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thanh to\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_4_Van_chuyen_hang_ve_Viet_Nam\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: V\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Sau khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n giao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn kho c\u1ee7a NHBLogistics t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u00f4ng ty s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i v\u00e0 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng qua h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng.<\/p>\n<h4><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Buoc_5_Nhan_hang_tai_Viet_Nam\"><\/span>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: Nh\u1eadn h\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<p>Khi h\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn kho t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn h\u00e0ng. NHBLogistics c\u0169ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 giao h\u00e0ng t\u1eadn n\u01a1i n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u.<\/p>\n<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_luu_y_khi_mua_ho_hang_hoa_tu_Han_Quoc\"><\/span>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi mua h\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng h\u00f3a t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h4 data-pm-slice=\"1 3 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Chon_nguon_hang_uy_tin\"><\/span>Ch\u1ecdn ngu\u1ed3n h\u00e0ng uy t\u00edn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-4043 gallery-columns-3 gallery-size-thumbnail'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/cac-web-order-hang-han-quoc-duoc-ua-chuong-nhblogistic-com\/naver-shopping\/'><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Naver-Shopping-150x150.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Naver-Shopping-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Naver-Shopping-120x120.jpg 120w, https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Naver-Shopping-370x370.jpg 370w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" \/><\/a>\n\t\t\t<\/div><\/figure><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/cac-web-order-hang-han-quoc-duoc-ua-chuong-nhblogistic-com\/11street-2\/'><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https:\/\/nhblogistics.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/11Stre