o l\u00e2u?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n trung b\u00ecnh t\u1eeb 5-7 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. V\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u1ecfa t\u1ed1c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 2-3 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Co_the_dat_hang_so_luong_lon_khong\"><\/span>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h5>\n<ul>\n<li>C\u00f3. NHBLogistics h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eb7t h\u00e0ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua s\u1ec9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dich_vu_co_ho_tro_doi_tra_hang_khong\"><\/span>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h5>\n<ul>\n<li>NHBLogistics c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng t\u00f9y v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng nh\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t sinh th\u00eam.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h5><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lam_the_nao_de_theo_doi_don_hang\"><\/span>L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h5>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean website NHBLogistics ho\u1eb7c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 CSKH \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00f4ng tin.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2824\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2824\" style=\"width: 700px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2824\" src=\"https:\/\/nhblogistic